{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c5e44e7427","title":"中国共产党上海市委员会宣传部关于右派分子著译的处理法","origin":"上海市档案馆，A22-1-305，第11页","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"54f37dc4a1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"c5e44e7427"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"202079a238","type":"title","text":"中国共产党上海市委员会宣传部关于右派分子著译的处理法","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"fb39426874","type":"subtitle","text":"[请白部长批改报到处　21/8]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"25806c77a1","type":"appellation","text":"中央宣传部：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"bea7f64715","type":"paragraph","text":"据上海市出版局反映，开展反右派斗争以来，读者纷纷要求书店停售右派分子著译的书笈，各有关出版社也来请示右派分子著译的处理法。经我们研究之后，提出以下意见：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"4203c8cfb2","type":"paragraph","text":"1、已经出版，现在书店发售的右派分子著译，一律暂不处理，但原出版单位应再审阅，如论点反动、错误，应结合反右派斗争进行驳斥和批判；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"d35e52ffc3","type":"paragraph","text":"2、右派分子尚未出版书稿，不论已否付印，不论用本名或笔名，可暂缓出版；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"c9c189d9db","type":"paragraph","text":"3、右派分子著译的书笈，一般暂不重印，如读者急需，其内容经审阅无问题，可酌量重印。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"19ecdcb426","type":"paragraph","text":"作以上处理的暂以已登报的右派分子为限。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"3d0429aff8","type":"paragraph","text":"以上意见，是否有当，请予指示。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"2ed6108942","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"},{"id":"aaefb2ce61","type":"paragraph","text":" 敬礼中共上海市委宣传部1957.8.21","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427"}],"page":{"id":"149d2860d6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5e44e7427","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}